ess.org/support/plugin/w3-total-cache/reviews/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">on the WordPress Plugin Repository</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></p>\n<p>Once again, we are sending a big thanks to all of our supporters, including those who are active in the forums helping end-users.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/W3EDGE?a=t5kXwTNLC-c:MOWIJpQbZ7A:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/W3EDGE?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/W3EDGE?a=t5kXwTNLC-c:MOWIJpQbZ7A:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/W3EDGE?i=t5kXwTNLC-c:MOWIJpQbZ7A:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/W3EDGE?a=t5kXwTNLC-c:MOWIJpQbZ7A:F7zBnMyn0Lo\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/W3EDGE?i=t5kXwTNLC-c:MOWIJpQbZ7A:F7zBnMyn0Lo\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/W3EDGE?a=t5kXwTNLC-c:MOWIJpQbZ7A:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/W3EDGE?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/W3EDGE?a=t5kXwTNLC-c:MOWIJpQbZ7A:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/W3EDGE?i=t5kXwTNLC-c:MOWIJpQbZ7A:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/W3EDGE/~4/t5kXwTNLC-c\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"https://www.w3-edge.com/weblog/2020/05/w3-total-cache-v0-14-1-patch-released/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17: